'''Remograph AB''' is a privately held company providing products and services for the [[computer graphics]], visual simulation and [[3D modeling]] industries. The company was founded in 2005 and has since then developed and marketed its [[Remo 3D]] product, a 3D modeling tool focused on supporting creation of 3D models intended for realtime visualization. Apart from their own product, Remograph also develops custom software for end-users and developers of e.g. visual simulation systems, visual databases or [[virtual reality]] applications. Remograph is situated in [[Linköping]], [[Sweden]].

